Program: Outlook
Title: Junior Smart - gang member to mentor
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p010hb73
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 21 Nov 2012
Matthew Bannister talks to Junior Smart, the London street gang member who served his time and now helps other young offenders get back on track. Also, Father Paolo Cugini, the Italian priest who spent the last 14 years working in poverty-stricken villages in Brazil, now preparing to return to Italy. Show less